    "Thus, it has been confirmed that the designed human motion intention prediction mechanism attained higher computational efficiency than the conventional models.",
    "Clinical relevance and practical implicationsThe developed AH-CNN-LSTM and AH-CNN-Res-LSTM models help in the human motion intention prediction process.",
